#: main0208.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0208.xhp\n"
"par_id3153414\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Status Bar contains information about the current document and offers various buttons with special functions."
msgstr "狀態列包含有關目前文件的資訊，並提供各種具有特殊功能的按鈕。"

